Malcolm X came out in November of 1992, 31 years ago this week. I was fortunate that Spike Lee selected me to compose the music exploring the historic life of Malcolm X.  This film, my 2nd, challenged me (perhaps it was the 70-piece orchestra) and set me on my path. 

Thank you @officialspikelee 
