I enjoyed reconnecting with friends and performing at the Kennedy Center Honors. Don't miss the #KCHonors  this Wednesday, December 27th at 8pm ET/8pm PT on CBS. 

Honorees for lifetime artistic achievements include actor and comedian Billy Crystal; acclaimed soprano Renée Fleming; British singer-songwriter producer, and member of the Bee Gees, Barry Gibb; rapper, singer, and actress Queen Latifah; and singer Dionne Warwick. 

